c3b421ea-f607-4fce-8b3c-1718aaae63a7/3410-1
00:23:11.436 --> 00:23:13.237
<v Lina Čeponienė>ėjau ten vis dar daugiau už nulis.</v>

c3b421ea-f607-4fce-8b3c-1718aaae63a7/3468-0
