c3b421ea-f607-4fce-8b3c-1718aaae63a7/3795-0
00:25:42.367 --> 00:25:44.877
<v Lina Čeponienė>Tai aš viską parodysiu vat kaip?</v>

c3b421ea-f607-4fce-8b3c-1718aaae63a7/3806-0
00:25:45.877 --> 00:25:49.147
