c3b421ea-f607-4fce-8b3c-1718aaae63a7/8624-0
01:01:08.327 --> 01:01:08.747
<v Lina Čeponienė>Negalima.</v>

c3b421ea-f607-4fce-8b3c-1718aaae63a7/8633-0
01:01:10.277 --> 01:01:13.247
<v Lina Čeponienė>Vadinasi,
