c3b421ea-f607-4fce-8b3c-1718aaae63a7/10926-0
01:18:34.337 --> 01:18:35.667
<v Lina Čeponienė>Vat šita dalis.</v>

c3b421ea-f607-4fce-8b3c-1718aaae63a7/10929-0
01:18:36.447 --> 01:18:37.297
